<br>
Personally I would rather develop the technologies so we better understand them. If we ignore them, or forbid them, we will have that stupid shocked look on our faces in the 1/10 of a second we have before the blast vaporizes us. <br>
<br>
Someone will do it, better it is us.  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
